WEBVTT

00:04:27.725 --> 00:04:30.137
But to teach children is very easy.

00:04:30.137 --> 00:04:32.328
And children will not do 
what we ask them to

00:04:32.548 --> 00:04:34.250
but they will do what we do.

00:04:35.043 --> 00:04:38.131
Anyone who messes 
with nature will be driven to dust.

00:04:38.464 --> 00:04:43.307
I tell children to start 
an adult literacy programme.

00:04:44.447 --> 00:04:48.199
Each one teach one.
Each child teach an adult.

00:04:48.820 --> 00:04:51.743
The right thinking.

00:04:52.023 --> 00:04:54.958
If this happens, 
everything will be alright.

00:04:55.577 --> 00:04:58.958
If we do that, 
believe me our rivers

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:00.952
will be as clean as they were.